### Denote (Zettelkasten) — `C-c n` Prefix
| Key | Command | Description |
|-----|---------|-------------|
| `C-c n n` | `denote-open-or-create` | Create or open a Denote note |
| `C-c n f` | `consult-notes` | Fuzzy search note titles |
| `C-c n s` | `consult-notes-search` | Full-text search in all notes (rg) |
| `C-c n i` | `denote-link-or-create` | Insert link to a note |
| `C-c n l` | `denote-find-link` | Find a note by its links |
| `C-c n b` | `denote-backlinks` | View backlinks for current note |
| `C-c n r` | `denote-rename-file` | Rename note file |
| `C-c n j` | `denote-journal-entry` | Create/open today's journal entry |
| `C-c n e ...` | **Explore Sub-prefix** | Random notes, statistics, etc. |

